examples.en: The great bird hovered high above our heads.
The fear of a new war hovered over us.
The UFO hovered for a while, then vanished into nothing.
...the hummingbird whirred as it hovered over a flower...
Her younger brother hovered in the background watching us.
A dragonfly hovered, vibrating and iridescent
The eagle hovered, ready to swoop at any moment.
